                    <li><a href="#" class="document-link"><i class="fas fa-file-pdf"></i> Document 5.pdf</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#" class="document-link"><i class="fas fa-file-pdf"></i> Document 6.pdf</a></li>
                  
                </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- reports section starts from here      -->
          <div class="content" id="reports">
            <h1>Reports</h1>
            <div id="rep">
                <p>Welcome to the Reports section. This is where you can access and review various reports and data analysis.</p>
                
                <h2>Monthly Sales Report</h2>
                <p>The monthly sales report provides an overview of our sales performance for the current year. It includes data on revenue, expenses, and profit margins.</p>
                
                <h2>Website Traffic Analysis</h2>
                <p>Our website traffic analysis report offers insights into user behavior on our website. It tracks metrics such as page views, bounce rate, and user demographics.</p>
                
                <h2>Customer Satisfaction Survey</h2>
                <p>We regularly conduct customer satisfaction surveys to gather feedback from our clients. The survey report summarizes the responses and highlights areas for improvement.</p>
                
                <!-- Add more report descriptions here as needed -->
        
                <p>Feel free to click on the reports below to access the detailed information:</p>
                <ul id="report-list">
                    <li><a href="#" class="report-link">Monthly Sales Report</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#" class="report-link">Website Traffic Analysis</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#" class="report-link">Customer Satisfaction</a></li>
